{
  "stem": "15694.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But we didn't know that that time, of course.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we didn't trust it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I accepted-- suddenly accepted the work in the ammunition camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And shortly before-- on the 24th-- on the 24th of August was the first transport from Bochnia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On the 22nd, I managed to take my father with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And also, we discussed a hiding place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, we had no tools.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had no material.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So in my book-- I'm not sure if I should show it to you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I show it to you in a minute.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In my book, I have the sketch of the-- illustrated the hiding place where Mother and sister stayed overnight.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was the triangular part above the entrance porch, which you could reach from the attic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a bungalow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the entrance to which we had a-- a piece of cardboard and put it so nobody can see that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, somebody walking up the stairs looking into the attic, he finds it empty.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "A thorough judge-- as-- a-- a thorough search would, of course, not stop anybody to finding the hiding place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now, before that, I have to sort of-- for a certain reason which will be apparent later, I have to switch back again.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Where I worked, we could find enough pieces of wood which I took back home in order not to suffer what we suffered the--the winter before, a shortage of material for-- for-- for a stove and warmth.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And every time I came home, I was sort of proud that I could pad the heap behind the house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "At one time, I-- my bundle was much too big.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I couldn't get into the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
